{"tid":1069677,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"丹素華盛頓之子主演Nolan神秘新作","createTime":"2019-03-20T06:26:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T10:45:02.000Z","uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3f15e1b354098c9a031787aa813ba8016086de41","tid":1069677,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T06:26:23.000Z","msg":"約翰大衛華盛頓（John David Washington）雖然自幼就曾參與父親丹佐華盛頓（Denzel Washington）主演的電影，但近兩年才可以說是正式在大銀幕上展露頭角，尤其去年主演了史派克李（Spike Lee）獲得坎城影展評審團大獎的《黑色黨徒》（BlacKkKlansman），又讓他得到了更廣泛的關注，而根據 Variety 報導，接下來他將主演克里斯多福諾蘭（Christopher Nolan）執導新作。<br />\n<br />\n克里斯多福諾蘭最近才剛完成了這部未命名新作的劇本，但在釋出任何確切細節之前，華納兄弟影業已經搶先為這部電影排定在 2020 年 7 月上映，而根據 Vareity 的消息來源透露，此片將會是一部龐大、創新的動作鉅片，同時也會再一次以 IMAX 展示給觀眾。<br />\n<br />\n約翰大衛華盛頓在 2018 年除了以《黑色黨徒》提名金球獎戲劇類電影最佳男主角、演員工會獎最佳男主角之外，其他演出電影還包括《Monsters and Men》、《Monster》兩部日舞影展作品，以及勞勃瑞福（Robert Redford）息影之作《老人與槍》（The Old Man &amp; the Gun），可說是曝光度相當密集。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://mediad.publicbroadcasting.net/p/shared/npr/styles/x_large/nprshared/201808/637839236.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmediad.publicbroadcasting.net%2Fp%2Fshared%2Fnpr%2Fstyles%2Fx_large%2Fnprshared%2F201808%2F637839236.jpg&h=85de547c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aca96c906e28203aae47c59d57b23674a44266a0","tid":1069677,"uid":19113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T10:26:00.000Z","msg":"仲有兩個confirm參與演出<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://variety.com/2019/film/news/elizabeth-debicki-robert-pattinson-christopher-nolan-1203168128/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2019%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Felizabeth-debicki-robert-pattinson-christopher-nolan-1203168128%2F&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9GyAt0yGCUsyxQooKadsmXE%3D&h=81232a62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://variety.com/2019/film/news/elizabeth-debicki-robert-pattinson-christopher-nolan-1203168128/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fBDaAwq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfBDaAwq.png&h=a692ca42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d77b5fee7e6a098bc7060385807dbc20b3b4ab5","tid":1069677,"uid":134757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T10:45:02.000Z","msg":"Give me akira"}]}